{
  "stem": "22237.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he would have a newspaper on his lap so that when they did come in, which happened every once in a while, he would-- he didn't work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They checked up on him, and we were always afraid that they would check.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because if they would have seen him working, they would take him away right away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what he did for us in order to make a living-- he still had to make a living-- he would-- in the evening when it got dark, he would put on a big overcoat and hide the bags, the leather bags, under his overcoat and visit his customers and sell some of these bags, what we call under the table, so to say.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this is how he made his living.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And meanwhile, my sister brought in some money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was repairing rugs, the sister, my middle sister, and I was sewing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I made alterations for people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my brother also had a job in Frankfurt in a-- in an office.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Nazis?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really have to think about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, I think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were not just Jews, they were Jews that came to Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And yes, I would say that they were treated worse than the German Jews around that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on, everybody was treated the same as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I'm talking now about starting with 1933, and all the way up to maybe 1937.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then everybody was treated alike.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I seem-- I remember that they started taking the situation seriously when my father couldn't continue working, because then times got very bad.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a very hard time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just didn't have enough money to pay their rent, to pay for food.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
